# SYNAPSE_CHANNEL — source-distribution manifest
#
# Tests are exercised in CI and live in the Git repository, not in the
# installable source distribution. setuptools' default sdist picks up the
# test_*.py modules but not their helper modules, conftest, or fixtures, which
# shipped a partial test suite that could not run (external review finding 7).
# Prune it so the sdist is a clean, installable library that mirrors the wheel.
prune tests
